61 serve for a term of four years, shall be appointed by the
62 Governor as follows:
63 (1) Seven members recommended by the Alabama
64 Association of 911 Districts, one from each of the seven
65 congressional districts, with each district representative
66 recommended selected by vote of the Alabama Association of 911
