170 (9) To establish a certification program to train and
171 certify public safety telecommunicators employed by a primary
172 PSAP receiving 911 calls, including establishing minimum core
173 competency topics and minimum number of training hours,
174 deciding whether a written examination is required, and
175 establishing any necessary certification requirements, to the
